      },
      "date": "2019-06-10 16:36:14.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nNathaniel, \"Gerrit Gatekeeper\" is no longer being used. Patches that have two positive reviews and Verified +1 from Jenkins and Maloo (and no unlanded patch dependencies) will automatically appear in a list for Oleg to land.\n\nThe patches that are ready are added to \"master-next\" and receive an additional 3-5 days integration testing before landing. So in the worst case, a patch may be waiting up to a week before being added to master-next.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
